        "reaction_type": "加氢处理反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydroprocessing reaction",
        "description": "在固定床反应器中，使用Pt@SOD-NiMo-SiO₂-Al₂O₃催化剂对麻风树油进行加氢转化，生产航空生物燃料。反应条件包括温度380-440°C，压力100 bar，H₂/进料比2200 (vol/vol)，液时空速1 h⁻¹。",
        "text_snippet": "Experimental results showed platinum encapsulated sulfided nickel and molybdenum supported on silica-alumina (Pt@SOD-NiMo(S)-SiO₂-Al₂O₃) had a substantial effect on the product composition, yield, and hydrogen consumption compared with the conventional NiMo(S)/SiO₂-Al₂O₃ catalyst for the hydroconversion reaction of jatropha oil to produce carbon–neutral green fuels.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢处理反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydroprocessing reaction",
        "description": "在固定床反应器中，使用常规NiMo/SiO₂-Al₂O₃催化剂对麻风树油进行加氢转化，作为对比实验。反应条件与实验1相同。",
        "text_snippet": "compared with the conventional NiMo(S)/SiO₂-Al₂O₃ catalyst for the hydroconversion reaction of jatropha oil",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
